                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150215-58-off340 t18150215-58-cd341"></join>, a great coat, value 5 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18150215-58-victim498" type="victimName">
                     Robert 
                     Edwards
                  <interp inst="t18150215-58-victim498" type="surname" value="Edwards"></interp>
